{"tid":525043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"VR中體驗觸覺　這只手套能感受虛擬物件質感！","createTime":"2018-01-10T08:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-11T04:37:33.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"56033320f6d40ddea22c710e58df8eab7d243580","tid":525043,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T08:23:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2C2_kbjtjRU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2C2_kbjtjRU&d=0F%2F3G%2BKy%2F4cf3VPMUpUJ2ZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=4d8e4ccc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2C2_kbjtjRU</a><br />\n2017/12/26 00:04<br />\n <br />\n虛擬實境（VR）技術帶給使用者在3D虛擬世界全新的視覺、聽覺體驗，但卻無法提供觸覺的感受，現在美國西雅圖的HaptX公司或將解決這個使用者長久以來的期待，將推出能在虛擬空間觸碰物件的VR手套「HaptX Gloves」，透過觸覺與力道回饋、動作追蹤，使用者就能摸出VR中物件的材質、大小等。<br />\n這只手套採用微流體（microfluidic）智能材質，有超過100個點可讓觸碰到的空氣膨脹、取代皮膚的感知，同時搭配動作追蹤技術，決定該送出何種觸覺回饋與阻力到使用者指間的感應面板上，Haptx執行長Jake Rubin補充，其專有的演算法能模擬與任何虛擬物件的互動，手套不靠電子式的驅動，而是微流體材質。<br />\n根據在2017 VRX體驗的媒體表示，配戴HaptX Gloves時，手套以管線接上一個控制氣體流動的盒子，能感受到手乘稻穀、雨水流體、或動物的觸感，但目前為原型版，一次只能處理一只手套，未來將能令雙手都感受到VR物件，Jake Rubin表示，目前已經與遊樂場、主題公園等娛樂方面的進行洽談，希望最快2018年就能出貨。HaptX創立於2012年，現已獲得包含VR投資公司、前推特CEO、迪士尼執行高層等900萬美金的投資。（廖家葆／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"f9ac7dc0c5d26520621011fc42d20c2071137ef3","tid":525043,"uid":55269,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T08:26:14.000Z","msg":"日本VR全面引入呢種技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457b3428632559a162db4e19e4c77c88424ae80e","tid":525043,"uid":4942,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T08:27:38.000Z","msg":"包住條jj同隻手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以後唔再需要女朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea1508f8464766d4af68649219e2cd49bef3f20","tid":525043,"uid":27143,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T08:28:54.000Z","msg":"只你老母咩"},{"pid":"a90911b3318d31480ff704e9410226fc2ef45ed5","tid":525043,"uid":153168,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T08:29:44.000Z","msg":"遲D會唔會有VR suit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4e821ba1586ce0f36af323828c0ff373e8548dc","tid":525043,"uid":39750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T08:30:09.000Z","msg":"用黎玩VRchat 正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef757f35249e63034a9a34ea44bb9e63447c4b8","tid":525043,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T08:41:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>只你老母咩</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只你老母</span>"},{"pid":"5e2a7fe6397c93544d83b2de57767c629a7c45fc","tid":525043,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T08:43:30.000Z","msg":"vr比人斬手指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f18640018e67f15b9aef36009bc417a6b7a232","tid":525043,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T10:23:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2847587459a62f8d9a870561d48cc8bc88ec4d64","tid":525043,"uid":14073,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f9ac7dc0c5d26520621011fc42d20c2071137ef3","tid":525043,"uid":55269,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T08:26:14.000Z","msg":"日本VR全面引入呢種技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T10:39:08.000Z","msg":"當男人唔再比女人煩，人類應該好快征服宇宙"},{"pid":"58889c3c4c25e4b494624330b50de9267a3a44f6","tid":525043,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T11:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66cc8e8a9486fc2816d784cbea06267